  "title": "Senior QS/ Quantity Surveyor [HQ Tender New MRT/ Pub projects]/ 5 day/ A1 maincon MNC/ Boon Keng/ receive yr end bonus are welcome",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Up to $7,000 Basic+ Variable bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Permanent position/ 5 work days/ Boon Keng area.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Having QS tendering experience in civil infrastructure/ Tunnel/ MRT/ PUB projects preferred.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Our client is a reputable MNC and a leading A1 main contractor, diverse in civil and building projects.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Reporting to Contract manager and involving in HQ tenders projects</li>\n  <li>Responsible for all work related to building Quantity Surveyor duties.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with consultants and subcontractors on the progress claim.</li>\n  <li>Prepare subcontract documents and purchasing agreements.</li>\n  <li>Preparing cost estimation and identifying variation works.</li>\n  <li>To source quotations from sub-contractors and prepare cost comparisons, negotiate, and award contracts</li>\n  <li>Variation order or EOT claims</li>\n  <li>Liaise with the project site, subcontractors, and contractual issues</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/ Degree in construction management/ Quantity Surveying or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years in building construction projects is preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>To apply please click on the APPLY button or email your resume to </strong><a href=\"mailto:search84@searchindex.com.sg\"><strong>search84@searchindex.com.sg</strong></a><strong> with the following details:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Reason for leaving each past &amp; current employment</li>\n  <li>Salary drawn for each past &amp; current employment</li>\n  <li>Expected Salary</li>\n  <li>Earliest availability date</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>Lionel Cheow</p>\n<p>EA License | 14C7092</p>\n<p>EA Registration Number | R1105005</p>",
